<li><a href="/wiki/Niddah" title="Niddah">Niddah</a></li>
<li><span title="Hebrew-language romanization"><i lang="he-Latn"><a href="/wiki/Pidyon_haben" title="Pidyon haben">Pidyon haben</a></i></span></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Kashrut" title="Kashrut">Kashrut</a></li>
